{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031203033977127611f2064eec","session_id":"1d2d8267-2c0d-47e7-bff0-9a3d28a3cbdc","message":{"id":"2026031203033977127611f2064eec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Phase 6 Code Review for F-002\n\n### 1. Spec Compliance Review\n\n**US-1: Pipeline Command** ✅\n- `/pipeline run/status/logs/stop` implemented in `handlers/pipeline.js`\n- `/planner` implemented in `handlers/planner.js` as type=planner\n- Alias `/p` for pipeline in `pipelineMeta.aliases`\n\n**US-2: Bugfix Command** ✅\n- `/bugfix <target>` in `handlers/bugfix.js`\n- Delegates to `handlePipeline` with `type: 'bugfix'`\n- Alias `/b` in `bugfixMeta.aliases`\n- Missing target returns error message\n\n**US-3: Status Query** ✅\n- `/status` in `handlers/status.js`\n- Returns pipeline list or \"no running pipelines\" message\n- Alias `/s` in `statusMeta.aliases`\n\n**US-4: Logs Query** ✅\n- `/logs [target]` in `handlers/logs.js`\n- FILE_THRESHOLD = 4000 chars (matches D3 decision)\n- Alias `/l` in `logsMeta.aliases`\n- Chunked sending for long logs\n\n**US-5: Stop Pipeline** ✅\n- `/stop [target]` in `handlers/stop.js`\n- Returns confirmation message\n\n**US-6: Error Guidance** ✅\n- `formatter.js` provides formatted error messages with suggestions\n- `validator.js` generates validation errors with suggestions\n\n**US-7: Authorization Guard** ✅\n- `isAuthorized()` in `index.js` calls `isAllowedUser()`\n- Unified rejection message (D2 decision)\n\n### 2. Code Quality Findings"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde47c4c2a40781ac14ef9fd27fd0","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:03:47.994Z","_requestId":"64ee86a8c26142b1a672413fdc3c1eb2"}
